results.title: Daken: Dark Wolverine #6
results.description: Daken's plans to undermine the criminal underworld of?Madipoor are falling into place!  But will the most dangerous men and women in the world simply topple where they stand -- or will Daken find the tables turned...and his neck in a noose?
